      'Set up Jenkins pipelines triggered by GitHub pushes with Maven build and automated deployment.',
      'Containerized backend, frontend, and database services with Docker and Docker Compose.',
      'Automated deployment to Ubuntu VM using secure transfer and scripted service restart.',
      'Tested manual Kubernetes deployment flow (Pods, Deployments, Services).',
